file.name: scenario_19_rs.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: refComponent
  description: refComponent
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: http://petstore.{host}.io/v1
    description: The production API server
    variables:
      host:
        default: openapi
        description: this value is assigned by the service provider
  - url: https://{subdomain}.swagger.io:{port}/{basePath}
    description: The production API server
    variables:
      subdomain:
        default: petstore
        description: this value is assigned by the service provider
      port:
        enum:
          - '8443'
          - '443'
        default: '443'
      basePath:
        default: v2
paths:
  /pets:
    post:
      summary: Creates a new pets.
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/User'
          # These two error responses have the same schema
        '400':
          description: Bad request
          content:
            application/xml:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
        '404':
          description: Not found
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
components:
  schemas:
    User:
      type: object
      required:
        - userName
      properties:
        userName:
          type: string
        firstName:
          type: string
        lastName:
          type: string
    Error:
      type: object
      required:
        - userName
      properties:
        userName:
          type: string
        firstName:
          type: string
        lastName:
          type: string

Error: notImplemented: path "/pets": post: responses: 400: contents: unsupported content types: [application/xml]
